: "2026-07-12T08:12:18", "influence": 1291.3, "repost_count": 61, "like_count": 3401, "comment_count": 420, "title": "这场赛后可能还有争议。 贝林厄姆打入的那粒扳平进球，挪威守门员开大脚，球先击中了"}, {"author": "Njone足球梦想", "platform": "知乎", "verification_type": "普通用户", "publish_time": "2026-07-12T14:55:32", "influence": 90.9, "repost_count": 0, "like_count": 203, "comment_count": 60, "title": "世界杯四强凑齐了——法国、西班牙、英格兰、阿根廷。国际足联排名前四，一个不差。挪"}, {"author": "A-Promised-Land1", "platform": "微博", "verification_type": "认证个人", "publish_time": "2026-07-12T14:57:38", "influence": 84.6, "repost_count": 14, "like_count": 202, "comment_count": 20, "title": "越是稀烂的国家，越输不起。埃及队输给阿根廷之后，毫无底线地攻击当值裁判，认为人家"}, {"author": "英仙说", "platform": "知乎", "verification_type": "认证个人", "publish_time": "2026-07-12T12:34:49", "influence": 51.4, "repost_count": 0, "like_count": 128, "comment_count": 26, "title": "其实英阿的历史恩怨，早就清了。头一波，是马岛战争+86世界杯。带英赢了热战，输了"}, {"author": "如约而至D_", "platform": "微博", "verification_type": "头部认证个人", "publish_time": "2026-07-12T17:25:10", "influence": 7.2, "repost_count": 0, "like_count": 24, "comment_count": 0, "title": "【#哈兰德父亲接连开炮#】#哈兰德父亲怒称被抢劫了# 哈兰德父亲：裁判救了英格兰"}], "platform_chain": {"nodes": [{"name": "知乎", "count": 6, "first_seen": "2026-07-10T14:50:52"}, {"name": "微博", "count": 5, "first_seen": "2026-07-12T08:12:18"}, {"name": "新浪新闻", "count": 8, "first_seen": "2026-07-12T08:37:45"}, {"name": "澎湃新闻", "count": 1, "first_seen": "2026-07-12T08:59:00"}], "links": [{"source": "知乎", "target": "微博", "value": 5}, {"source": "微博", "target": "新浪新闻", "value": 8}, {"source": "新浪新闻", "target": "澎湃新闻", "value": 1}]}}', '2026-07-13 19:10:32', '2026-07-13 19:10:32');
